  [ 88] getprop 1060 ............................ <pSitCounter>
  [ 91] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <pSitCounter>
  [ 93] extcall 706 ............................. CounterReset(pSitCounter)
  [ 96] pop 1 ................................... end case
